namespace Interval

features
	Interval {featureDescription__ "interval describes a point in time when something is triggered.", abstract true}
		or
			Immediately {featureDescription__ "means as soon as possible (e.g. after every recognized change)"}
			Manually {featureDescription__ "means only when the user pushes a button (or something similar)"}
